[One can hope that the UWA team investigating the KVNP situation comes up
with a confirmed diagnosis quicker than what happened earlier this year in
the QENP. Their financial situation sounds uncertain, and the northern
parts of the country are afflicted with fighting and armies of brigands,
not the easiest of situations, even on a good day. - Mod.MHJ]
